public class GenericStoredDynamicEntitiesQuery<C>
extends AbstractJdbcWorker
implements EntitiesQuery<Object>, CriteriaDependent<C>, OrderedFieldsContainer, NamedFieldsContainer, OrderedNamedFieldsContainer, TransformationSpec

GenericStoredDynamicEntitiesQuery is a query that has its SQL query statement stored in a resource file and also implements the interface EntitiesQuery. Alternatively, the SQL query can be supplied on as a String along with a (unique) id.
The type of entity returned by the getEntity() method is created dynamically on runtime and contains the elements of the query columns. Therefore StoredDynamicEntitiesQuery is declared as EntitiesQuery
